<inglise> - every worker receives three weeks' paid annual leave in accordance with the conditions for the entitlement to, and granting of, such leave laid down by national legislation and/or practice, and </inglise>
<eesti> - iga t&ouml;&ouml;taja saab kolm n&auml;dalat iga-aastast tasulist puhkust vastavalt niisuguse puhkuse &otilde;iguse ja andmise tingimustele, mis on ette n&auml;htud siseriiklike &otilde;igusaktide ja/v&otilde;i tavadega. </eesti>
